20/02/2024

Buyer Business Requirement
Define the boundaries of the project, including what will be included and excluded
Users should be able to register, log in, and manage their accounts securely.
Organize products into categories and subcategories for easy navigation.
Allow users to add/remove items, update quantities, and proceed to checkout.
Calculate the total price, including taxes and shipping costs.
Support various payment methods (credit/debit cards, PayPal, etc.).
Ensure the website is accessible and user-friendly across devices (desktop, mobile, tablet).
Buyer System Requirement
Database Management System (DBMS): MySQL,
Programming Languages:  HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript and also frameworks like React
Version Control System: Git for managing codebase
Load Testing: Conduct load testing to ensure the system can handle peak loads

22/02/2024
Buyer User stories 
As a buyer, I want to easily search for products by category or keyword so that I can quickly find what I'm looking for.
As a buyer, I want to see detailed product descriptions, including specifications, sizes, and materials, so that I can make informed purchasing decisions.
As a buyer, I want to be able to view high-quality images of products from different angles to get a clear picture of what I'm buying.
As a buyer, I want to read reviews and ratings from other customers to gauge the quality and reliability of the products before making a purchase.
As a buyer, I want to add items to my shopping cart and easily adjust quantities or remove items as needed before proceeding to checkout.
As a buyer, I want to have multiple secure payment options available, such as credit/debit card, PayPal, or other trusted methods, to complete my purchase.
As a buyer, I want to track the status of my orders, including shipping updates and delivery estimates, so that I know when to expect my items.
As a buyer, I want to have the option to create an account for faster checkout in the future and to easily track my order history and manage returns or exchanges.
As a buyer, I want to receive personalized recommendations based on my past purchases and browsing history to discover new products that match my interests.
As a buyer, I want to be able to contact customer support easily if I have any questions or concerns about my order or the products offered on the website



